52:02.253 --> 52:04.153
- Goddammit, Oda Mae...
- Don't you goddammit me!

52:04.153 --> 52:06.154
Don't you take the
Lord's name in vain.

52:06.154 --> 52:07.954
- You understand?
- Would you relax?

52:07.954 --> 52:09.553
No, you relax!
You're the dead guy.

52:09.553 --> 52:12.053
You want me to help you?
You'd better apologise.

52:12.053 --> 52:14.153
- Curse!
- That's it, I'm leaving.

52:14.953 --> 52:17.452
Nobody talks to me like that.
You understand me?

52:18.152 --> 52:19.452
Now, you'd better apologise.

52:19.452 --> 52:20.652
I'm sorry.

52:20.652 --> 52:22.053
I apologise.

52:22.053 --> 52:23.553
OK?

52:23.553 --> 52:26.152
Now would you sit down?

52:26.452 --> 52:27.452
Please?

52:27.452 --> 52:29.453
He's apologised.

52:31.154 --> 52:32.954
I need you to tell
Molly what I'm saying

52:32.954 --> 52:34.954
but you have to
tell her word for word.

52:34.954 --> 52:37.253
All right?
Word for word.

52:37.553 --> 52:40.653
Yes. He wants me to
tell you what he's saying

52:40.653 --> 52:42.753
word for word.

52:48.053 --> 52:49.353
Molly, you're in danger.

52:49.353 --> 52:51.153
You can't just
blurt it out like that!

52:51.153 --> 52:52.554
And quit moving around

52:52.554 --> 52:53.653
you're start to make me dizzy.

52:53.653 --> 52:55.753
I'll just tell her
in my own way.

52:56.853 --> 52:58.453
Molly

52:58.453 --> 53:00.753
you're in danger, girl.

53:02.152 --> 53:03.652
What are you talking about?

53:03.752 --> 53:05.152
I know the
man who killed me.

53:05.152 --> 53:06.353
He knows the
man who killed him.

53:06.353 --> 53:09.254
His name is Willie Lopez,
and I know where he lives.

53:09.354 --> 53:11.353
His name is Willie Lopez,
he is Puerto-Rican.

53:11.353 --> 53:13.153
- He knows where he lives.
- Write it down.

53:13.153 --> 53:14.153
He wants you
to write it down.

53:14.153 --> 53:16.454
- You write it down.
- I ain't no damned secretary!

53:16.454 --> 53:18.254
Just do it!

53:20.653 --> 53:22.353
He is so testy!

53:23.353 --> 53:24.451
What is it you
want me to write?

53:24.451 --> 53:27.951
303, Prospect Place, apt. 4D.

53:27.951 --> 53:29.950
303 Prospect Place?

53:29.950 --> 53:31.650
Yes.

53:31.750 --> 53:32.951
It's my neighbourhood.

53:32.951 --> 53:34.951
Molly, he's got my wallet

53:35.151 --> 53:36.351
he's got my key

53:36.351 --> 53:38.150
and he was in here.

53:38.250 --> 53:40.251
he's got his wallet, and his key
and he was in here.

53:40.251 --> 53:41.951
Yesterday, when you came
back from your walk with Carl

53:41.951 --> 53:44.352
you went upstairs,
you talked to Floyd...

53:44.352 --> 53:45.452
All right, all right, all right.

53:45.452 --> 53:48.251
When you came in yesterday from
your walk with Carl, he was here.

53:48.251 --> 53:50.651
You checked your clothes
off, he saw everything.

53:50.651 --> 53:53.751
Molly, you got to go to the police.
It was a set-up.

53:53.751 --> 53:56.051
I was murdered.

53:56.651 --> 53:59.651
He wants you to go the police.
He said it was a set-up, he was murdered.

53:59.651 --> 54:00.650
Somebody else is involved...

54:00.750 --> 54:03.951
- I don't know who, but...
- Forget it. I don't want no more to do with this, OK.

54:03.951 --> 54:05.050
Wait.

54:05.150 --> 54:07.750
- Where are you going?
- What do you mean "where am I going"? I'm leaving.

54:07.750 --> 54:10.250
I did everything I said I was gonna do.
And don't be following me

54:10.250 --> 54:11.850
cause I'm finished.
And I mean it!

54:11.850 --> 54:13.749
Have a nice life,
have a nice death.

54:13.849 --> 54:15.549
Goodbye.

54:18.850 --> 54:21.051
Molly, there's no one
on earth besides you

54:21.251 --> 54:24.350
who'd want this to be
true more than me. But...

54:24.450 --> 54:26.650
You've got to be
rational about this.

54:26.750 --> 54:29.651
Sam is no more
in this room than...

54:30.551 --> 54:32.550
Look...

54:32.650 --> 54:35.550
I understand the
need to hang on to him

54:35.550 --> 54:37.150
I really do.

54:37.150 --> 54:38.550
But this is absurd!

54:38.550 --> 54:42.449
I know this seems absurd,
but it had to be real.

54:42.449 --> 54:44.650
How could you believe some
fortune-teller from Brooklyn

54:44.750 --> 54:46.450
who just shows
up at your door?

54:46.450 --> 54:49.649
I watched them
have a conversation.

54:49.749 --> 54:52.350
I don't buy it, Moll.
Not for a minute.

54:52.450 --> 54:54.551
What about the
things she knew?

54:54.951 --> 54:56.251
What things?

54:56.451 --> 54:59.850
The photo that Sam took
of me on our trip to Reno.

54:59.850 --> 55:01.850
Carl, we were alone.

55:02.250 --> 55:05.350
And the green underwear
that I wrote my name in.

55:08.750 --> 55:11.050
She said Sam knew who killed him.

55:12.750 --> 55:14.550
That he was set up.

55:14.550 --> 55:17.850
This is getting deranged.
We're going off the deep end here.

55:17.850 --> 55:19.950
- She had a name and an address.
- Good, Molly, good...

55:19.950 --> 55:24.050
Willie Lopez, 303
Prospect Place, apt. 4D.

55:25.649 --> 55:27.149
This is sick.

55:27.149 --> 55:28.349
Oh, Carl.

55:28.349 --> 55:30.250
This is really sick.

55:33.451 --> 55:34.650
Molly, I don't understand

55:34.650 --> 55:37.850
how you could...
could...

55:38.850 --> 55:41.351
swallow this crap.
I mean...

55:41.551 --> 55:44.150
This guy may not even exist.
This woman...

55:44.550 --> 55:45.750
Maybe she's just
trying to use you

55:45.750 --> 55:47.750
to set someone up.

55:48.950 --> 55:50.850
You're right.

55:51.050 --> 55:53.149
You're absolutely right.

55:53.749 --> 55:55.650
That's what I've
got to find out.

55:55.750 --> 55:58.150
What do you mean "find out"?
How are you gonna do that?

55:58.250 --> 56:00.649
She said Sam wants
me to go to the police.

56:00.649 --> 56:03.650
Sam wants you
to go to the police?

56:03.650 --> 56:05.751
Jesus, Moll!..

56:05.851 --> 56:07.051
Are you out of your mi...
I mean

56:07.051 --> 56:08.651
what are you gonna tell the police?
You gonna tell them

56:08.751 --> 56:11.450
that some storefront
psychic lady has been

56:11.850 --> 56:13.150
communing with the dead?

56:13.150 --> 56:14.450
Do you have any idea
how that sounds?

56:14.450 --> 56:17.750
You're talking ghosts here,
for Christ's sake.

56:19.650 --> 56:21.250
I'm sorry.

56:21.250 --> 56:23.949
This stuff just really
gets to me, you know.

56:24.049 --> 56:26.149
It's OK if you
don't believe me.

56:26.349 --> 56:28.649
I'm trying to, Molly.

56:32.349 --> 56:34.049
Look.

56:35.949 --> 56:37.548
If it'll make you
feel any better

56:37.748 --> 56:40.749
I'll go check this out, OK?

56:40.749 --> 56:42.950
I want you to try
and get some sleep.

56:44.150 --> 56:46.249
OK?

56:48.249 --> 56:49.349
I'll call you in the morning.

56:49.349 --> 56:51.550
- OK.
- All right. Goodnight.

57:18.750 --> 57:20.750
Be careful.

57:34.149 --> 57:35.649
Carl!

57:35.649 --> 57:37.649
What the hell are
you doing here?

57:39.949 --> 57:42.249
Who have you
been talking to, Willie?

57:42.249 --> 57:44.149
Talking to?
What the hell do you mean?

57:44.149 --> 57:45.549
Some woman
knows all about you.

57:45.549 --> 57:47.149
Everything.

57:47.149 --> 57:48.748
Where's she
getting it from?

57:48.748 --> 57:50.048
I haven't said
a word to anybody.

57:50.048 --> 57:53.049
She knows your name, goddammit.
She knows where you live.

57:53.049 --> 57:54.650
How do women
know where I live?

57:54.650 --> 57:56.250
This is not a joke!

57:56.250 --> 57:58.549
She knows about
the murder.

57:59.949 --> 58:01.749
Now, I want you
to find this bitch

58:01.749 --> 58:03.650
whoever she is

58:03.650 --> 58:05.749
and I want you to...

58:07.449 --> 58:09.949
Just get rid of her, OK?

58:10.549 --> 58:11.949
I've got 4 million dollars

58:11.949 --> 58:14.748
stuffed in a goddamn computer.

58:15.848 --> 58:17.448
If I don't get those codes

58:17.448 --> 58:19.749
if that money is not
transferred soon...

58:22.649 --> 58:24.248
l'm...

58:24.348 --> 58:25.448
dead.

58:25.448 --> 58:26.549
We're both dead.

58:26.549 --> 58:28.750
Why don't you tell them
you only launder money

58:28.750 --> 58:30.250
on the first of the month.

58:30.250 --> 58:32.749
What the hell is
wrong with you?

58:32.749 --> 58:35.049
ls everything a joke?

58:35.149 --> 58:36.349
You killed a man.

58:36.349 --> 58:38.649
You were supposed to steal
his wallet, was that joke?

58:38.749 --> 58:40.449
I did you a favour, man.

58:40.449 --> 58:42.349
That was a freebie.

58:43.049 --> 58:46.848
Look, these are
drug dealers, OK?

58:47.448 --> 58:49.248
Just don't blow
this for me, Willie.

58:49.248 --> 58:51.848
I'd lose my job, I'd go to jail.

58:52.448 --> 58:55.448
$80,000 of that money is mine.

58:58.148 --> 59:00.347
Look, just...

59:00.947 --> 59:02.347
Let me have the keys
to Sam's apartment

59:02.347 --> 59:05.749
I'll get the address
book myself, OK?

59:31.446 --> 59:33.546
You goddamn bastard!

59:33.546 --> 59:34.746
Why?

59:34.746 --> 59:37.746
Why?
You were my friend!

59:39.647 --> 59:42.047
I had a life, goddamn you!

59:42.347 --> 59:44.946
I had a life.

59:52.446 --> 59:55.446
Look, I don't even believe
in this stuff myself.

59:56.046 --> 59:58.446
But she was real.

59:58.846 --> 01:00:01.746
Do you think I'd come here
if it wasn't real?

01:00:03.646 --> 01:00:07.146
You told me if I had any new
information, that I should come.

01:00:08.346 --> 01:00:10.645
So, here I am.

01:00:14.345 --> 01:00:15.646
I know how this sounds.

01:00:15.646 --> 01:00:17.547
I mean, I hear
myself saying it

01:00:17.547 --> 01:00:20.146
and I wanna cringe.

01:00:20.446 --> 01:00:23.246
But this woman knew
things she couldn't have known.

01:00:23.646 --> 01:00:25.747
Things Sam only said to me.

01:00:25.847 --> 01:00:26.747
OK.

01:00:26.747 --> 01:00:29.346
According to this psychic lady

01:00:29.346 --> 01:00:33.046
there are ghosts and
spirits all over the place?

01:00:33.546 --> 01:00:36.146
Watching us all the time?

01:00:39.045 --> 01:00:41.946
Hell, I'm never going
to get undressed again.

01:00:42.746 --> 01:00:43.846
Excuse me.

01:00:43.846 --> 01:00:46.645
I've got more
important things to do.

01:00:57.346 --> 01:00:59.246
The guy's name is Willie Lopez.

01:00:59.546 --> 01:01:02.746
All I'm asking is for
you to check it out.

01:01:03.046 --> 01:01:05.346
OK. You just wait here

01:01:05.346 --> 01:01:08.845
and let me see if the
guy's got a record. All right?

01:01:08.845 --> 01:01:11.445
Right.

01:02:12.345 --> 01:02:14.445
What are you doing?

01:02:14.445 --> 01:02:17.545
- Where's the file on Willie Lopez?
- There's no file for Willie Lopez.

01:02:17.645 --> 01:02:19.345
He was probably
some old boyfriend

01:02:19.345 --> 01:02:21.845
she was trying
to get even with.

01:02:22.145 --> 01:02:26.145
And this psychic woman's got
a record that goes back a long way.

01:02:26.345 --> 01:02:29.445
1967, Shreveport.

01:02:29.445 --> 01:02:30.545
Forgery

01:02:30.545 --> 01:02:33.045
selling of false ID.

01:02:33.045 --> 01:02:35.744
Served one year in 1971.

01:02:35.944 --> 01:02:39.846
Baton Rouge. Arrested for
fraud, numbers racketeering.

01:02:39.846 --> 01:02:42.845
served ten months, 1974.

01:02:42.945 --> 01:02:44.845
Look, this is impossible!

01:02:45.245 --> 01:02:47.045
It goes on and on.

01:02:47.045 --> 01:02:50.046
She knew things -
private things.

01:02:50.146 --> 01:02:51.645
Now how could she
have known all that?

01:02:51.645 --> 01:02:53.545
A lot of times
they read the obits.

01:02:53.845 --> 01:02:57.445
All she had to do was see
the word "banker." Boom.

01:02:57.545 --> 01:03:00.444
They even go
through your garbage

01:03:00.444 --> 01:03:01.944
to find things they can use.

01:03:02.044 --> 01:03:03.845
Letters, old papers.

01:03:03.945 --> 01:03:05.845
It doesn't take much.

01:03:05.945 --> 01:03:07.945
No.

01:03:09.244 --> 01:03:11.945
It was real.

01:03:13.545 --> 01:03:18.445
She knew about
a sweater I knitted.

01:03:18.645 --> 01:03:21.145
And songs we sang.

01:03:25.745 --> 01:03:28.545
The trip to Montego Bay.

01:03:30.245 --> 01:03:31.544
I'm sorry.

01:03:31.544 --> 01:03:33.844
I know this is hard.

01:03:34.044 --> 01:03:35.845
People want so
much to believe.

01:03:35.845 --> 01:03:37.344
They're grieving

01:03:37.344 --> 01:03:39.344
they're vulnerable...

01:03:39.944 --> 01:03:42.244
And they will
give anything

01:03:42.344 --> 01:03:44.144
for one last moment.

01:03:44.144 --> 01:03:45.643
Believe me

01:03:45.643 --> 01:03:48.143
these people know
what they're doing.

01:03:48.643 --> 01:03:50.444
I know how you must feel

01:03:50.444 --> 01:03:53.645
but you know you
can press charges.

01:03:57.544 --> 01:03:59.345
No.

01:04:02.345 --> 01:04:04.244
Thank you.

01:04:18.144 --> 01:04:20.544
God, let this be it.

01:04:30.444 --> 01:04:32.144
Yeah.

01:04:32.944 --> 01:04:34.844
Yes.

01:04:46.544 --> 01:04:47.644
Hello.

01:04:47.644 --> 01:04:49.344
Eddie?
It's Carl Bruner.

01:04:49.344 --> 01:04:50.644
- What's up?
- We're fine.

01:04:50.644 --> 01:04:52.144
Everything's fine.
Just we're all set.

01:04:52.144 --> 01:04:54.744
- Good.
- Just let me know what you want me to do.

01:04:55.044 --> 01:04:57.843
I want you to transfer the money
from the 12 separate accounts

01:04:57.843 --> 01:05:01.044
into a single account
under the name "Rita Miller. "

01:05:01.044 --> 01:05:02.344
OK.

01:05:02.344 --> 01:05:04.345
Tomorrow, at five
minutes before closing

01:05:04.345 --> 01:05:06.044
3.55 pm

01:05:06.044 --> 01:05:09.944
transfer the full account to
the First lsland Bank of Nassau

01:05:09.944 --> 01:05:13.445
registry number
486-9580.

01:05:13.745 --> 01:05:15.644
Call us when it's done.

01:05:15.844 --> 01:05:17.644
OK, I've got it.

01:05:18.244 --> 01:05:20.242
Just tell Mr Balistrari

01:05:20.242 --> 01:05:22.242
that there won't be
any more problems, OK.

01:05:22.242 --> 01:05:23.541
- Yeah, I'll do that.
- Thank you.

01:05:23.641 --> 01:05:25.641
Good work, Carl.

01:06:24.942 --> 01:06:27.141
Molly, why can't
you hear me?

01:06:27.941 --> 01:06:30.141
I need you.

01:06:41.441 --> 01:06:42.541
Who is it?

01:06:42.541 --> 01:06:44.440
It's Carl, Molly.

01:06:44.440 --> 01:06:45.540
No.

01:06:45.540 --> 01:06:47.041
Don't open the
goddamn door!

01:06:47.041 --> 01:06:48.342
- He's a murderer.
- Hi.

01:06:48.342 --> 01:06:50.842
- Hey.
- Listen, sorry, I know it's late.

01:06:50.842 --> 01:06:53.541
I'm sorry to disturb you.
I just...

01:06:53.741 --> 01:06:55.541
I've been thinking
about you all day.

01:06:55.541 --> 01:06:59.341
And I feel really
lousy about last night.

01:06:59.541 --> 01:07:00.941
This supernatural thing...

01:07:01.041 --> 01:07:03.541
Listen, don't worry
about it, really. It's OK.

01:07:03.541 --> 01:07:04.541
No, it's not.

01:07:04.541 --> 01:07:07.441
You needed me to
hear you, and I didn't.

01:07:07.441 --> 01:07:09.541
I wasn't there for
you and that was...

01:07:10.241 --> 01:07:12.141
That was wrong.

01:07:12.341 --> 01:07:14.341
It's just... I...

01:07:15.041 --> 01:07:16.641
I just...

01:07:16.641 --> 01:07:19.640
I want you to know
that I'm your friend, Moll.

01:07:20.640 --> 01:07:21.640
Thanks, Carl.

01:07:21.640 --> 01:07:23.040
You were never her friend.

01:07:23.040 --> 01:07:24.741
That really means
a lot to me.

01:07:24.741 --> 01:07:25.942
Me too.

01:07:25.942 --> 01:07:28.141
So I've brought you some
Japanese apple pears.

01:07:28.141 --> 01:07:30.141
I know you like them.

01:07:31.941 --> 01:07:34.342
Thanks, that's very sweet.

01:07:34.342 --> 01:07:36.442
Could I come in for a second?

01:07:36.642 --> 01:07:38.841
I won't stay long.
it's just been one of those days.

01:07:38.941 --> 01:07:40.241
Maybe a cup of coffee?

01:07:40.241 --> 01:07:41.741
Yeah, come on in.

01:07:41.741 --> 01:07:43.841
No, Molly.

01:07:43.841 --> 01:07:45.841
You seem a little tense.

01:07:45.841 --> 01:07:46.840
Are you OK?

01:07:46.840 --> 01:07:48.840
No, I'm fine. It's just...

01:07:48.940 --> 01:07:51.241
What can I tell you?
It's been tough.

01:07:51.241 --> 01:07:53.141
You know.

01:07:53.141 --> 01:07:54.741
It just still hurts so much.

01:07:54.841 --> 01:07:56.740
You lying snake.

01:07:56.840 --> 01:07:59.742
And then on top of it,
there's stuff at work.

01:07:59.842 --> 01:08:01.842
They've given me my
own accounts, which is...

01:08:02.042 --> 01:08:03.642
wich is good, but I...

01:08:03.642 --> 01:08:06.841
I just haven't really
had time to adjust.

01:08:07.741 --> 01:08:09.941
To absorb everything.

01:08:12.940 --> 01:08:15.241
It's no big deal.

01:08:26.540 --> 01:08:28.439
Can I have a
little more cream?

01:08:28.740 --> 01:08:30.340
Yeah.

01:08:31.339 --> 01:08:32.538
Oh, shit!

01:08:32.538 --> 01:08:35.038
Jesus, I can't believe
I did that.

01:08:35.038 --> 01:08:37.341
- Are you all right?
- Yeah, I'm fine.

01:08:38.841 --> 01:08:39.939
Ah, God.

01:08:40.140 --> 01:08:41.439
Let me throw
that in the washer.

01:08:41.439 --> 01:08:44.140
Don't worry about it.
It's OK.

01:08:44.340 --> 01:08:46.041
Do you want me to
give you another shirt?

01:08:46.041 --> 01:08:48.241
No, it'll dry,
just take a minute.

01:08:54.340 --> 01:08:57.639
So where were you today? I thought
you were gonna come into the bank

01:08:57.639 --> 01:08:59.639
and sign those papers?

01:08:59.939 --> 01:09:02.240
Well, I was supposed to,
but I didn't have time.

01:09:03.439 --> 01:09:05.340
I went to the police.

01:09:12.041 --> 01:09:13.640
You did?

01:09:13.640 --> 01:09:15.041
Wow. What did you tell them?

01:09:15.041 --> 01:09:16.540
What did they say?

01:09:16.540 --> 01:09:18.840
It was awful.

01:09:19.240 --> 01:09:21.140
I felt really stupid.

01:09:22.439 --> 01:09:24.639
They brought out
a file on this woman

01:09:25.140 --> 01:09:27.040
at least ten inches thick.

01:09:27.740 --> 01:09:29.439
Rip-off artist, huh?

01:09:29.740 --> 01:09:31.640
No, Molly.

01:09:32.240 --> 01:09:35.140
You know, the sad thing

01:09:36.540 --> 01:09:38.540
is that I believed her.

01:09:38.540 --> 01:09:40.439
Molly

